issues.title: Severe performance regression in 1.8.6
issues.body:
I'm running this grammar:
https://github.com/joankaradimov/Magnetar/blob/master/MagnetarCraft/src/iscript_parser.cpp#L71
... with this input file:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/neivv/aice/master/test_scripts/vanilla.txt

On v1.8.5 I'm observing parse times of below 1 second. On 1.8.6 it's above 10 seconds.

Similarly -- on the [web playgound](https://yhirose.github.io/cpp-peglib/) I was running identical examples for under 150 ms the previous week. I'm assuming the version over there was updated these last couple of days, since the execution times are suddenly 1-2 orders of magnitude worse.
